data.description: Gorgeous 3BR/2BA split/open floor plan in Glen Laurel. This home boasts simulated hand scraped flooring in the great room, kitchen, breakfast area & foyer. Gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances including side by side refrigerator, granite counter-tops and mosaic tile back splash. Custom cabinets w/ indirect lighting. Hook your iPod or tablet up to the built in speakers to create the perfect atmosphere. Master suite with trey ceiling, walk-in closet, double vanity, glass enclosed shower & garden tub. Beautiful hand rubbed oil finished fixtures. 2 faux wood blinds throughout. Exterior features include stacked stone, covered patio, privacy fence, sprinkler system and 2 car garage. Subdivision features walking trail and playground for the little ones. Color scheme and details will vary. Photos are from similar home already built.
